{
  "stem": "7094.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm very grateful for that, because without it, I wouldn't find life-- very unbearable.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because it was the last words of my mother's.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was very difficult to impose it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, my difficulty with Frances was that-- that I was hoping, again, that she will understand and she will respond to it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I didn't find this response in that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is why I find it-- I'm very appreciative that I have-- that we have Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We meet every Friday, once in my place, once at their place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have Pesach.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have a tradition, our own.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe my grandfather and my father wouldn't approve of that, because they were very orthodox.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nonetheless, I think I would explain to them, and I think they would appreciate that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I'm very pleased that I have that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really mean it that it's very fundamental to my well-being.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To-- to-- I'm more relaxed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I hope that my other grandchildren-- Rebecca and Jonathan, who don't have the link with the Jewish community, who don't have the education, don't know very much about it-- that perhaps, in time, they will find-- out of curiosity-- they will learn something about it.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I always feel, why should they know all about Jesus Christ and not to know about Moses?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I hope that they will.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They are beautiful children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very bright, very intelligent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if Martin was alive, I know that he would want them to continue.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know that every Friday he would phone me up, and Rebecca, the three-year-old, would phone me also to wish me Shabbat shalom.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I know that there would have been a link.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I accept the situation, because Frances has their-- has her own attitude and her own way of bringing up the children.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
